course_description: In this course, students will continue to refine their team leadership and clinical management skills to manage acute and chronic illness, and injuries of infants, children and adolescents in specialty, inpatient, and emergency department settings.
prerequisites: NRSG 817D and NRSG 818D or equivalent transfer credit as prerequisites.
